OL,3,COrange Order urges 'PM in waiting'
OL,4,CBurnham to address 'challenges to the
OL,5,CUnion'
OL,7,FThe leadership of the Orange Order is
OL,8,Fpressing the man expected to become
OL,9,Fthe next Prime Minister, Andy Burnham,
OL,10,Fto address "challenges to the Union".
OL,12,FMr Burnham, as the only candidate in
OL,13,FLabour's leadership process, is
OL,14,Fexpected officially to succeed Sir
OL,15,FKeir Starmer as premier next Monday.
OL,17,FGrand Secretary of the Orange Order
OL,18,FRev Mervyn Gibson also lambasted the
OL,19,Fcurrent Secretary of State for
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland, Hilary Benn, as a
OL,21,F"huge disappointment".
OL,26,@rD@LOUrD@dO]}D@AOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
