PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783964952
OL,3,COrange Order urges 'PM in waiting'
OL,4,CBurnham to address 'challenges to the
OL,5,CUnion'
OL,7,FIt comes amid political turbulence at
OL,8,FStormont where the multi-party
OL,9,FExecutive has been unable to agree a
OL,10,Fbudget for this financial year, while
OL,11,Frecent elections saw nationalist First
OL,12,FMinisters returned in Scotland and
OL,13,FWales.
OL,15,FSpeaking to a July 12 parade gathering
OL,16,Fin Kilrea, Co Londonderry on Monday,
OL,17,FRev Gibson urged "better promotion of
OL,18,Fthe strengths and benefits of the
OL,19,FUnion".
OL,26,@yD@ROU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783964952
OL,3,COrange Order urges 'PM in waiting'
OL,4,CBurnham to address 'challenges to the
OL,5,CUnion'
OL,7,F"We need to share those realities with
OL,8,Fethnic communities, undecided voters,
OL,9,Fapathetic voters, non-voters, the
OL,10,Fyounger demographic who identity as
OL,11,Fconstitutionally neutral, those of
OL,12,Fdiffering faiths or none, and even
OL,13,Fsoft nationalists," he said.
OL,15,F"Those Unionists who thought that the
OL,16,FAlliance Party was the answer need to
OL,17,Fbe welcomed home.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@SO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783964952
OL,3,COrange Order urges 'PM in waiting'
OL,4,CBurnham to address 'challenges to the
OL,5,CUnion'
OL,7,F"Many of those we need to engage with
OL,8,Fmay not enjoy the sound of the Lambeg
OL,9,For don a sash, but that's the
OL,10,Fattraction of true Britishness, it
OL,11,Fembraces the principles of the
OL,12,FGlorious Revolution and practises
OL,13,F'Civil and Religious Liberty for all `
OL,14,Fspecial privileges for none'."
OL,16,FHe went on: "We plan to write to Andy
OL,17,FBurnham, the Prime Minister in
OL,18,Fwaiting, to outline what we believe is
OL,19,Fbest for Northern Ireland and the
OL,20,FUnited Kingdom.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@^O]xD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783964952
OL,3,COrange Order urges 'PM in waiting'
OL,4,CBurnham to address 'challenges to the
OL,5,CUnion'
OL,7,F"Yes, there are challenges for the
OL,8,FUnion ` we have three nationalist
OL,9,Fleaders in the devolved
OL,10,Fadministrations and there are obvious
OL,11,Fpolitical issues here in Northern
OL,12,FIreland."
OL,14,FRev Gibson said the answer to
OL,15,Fchallenges at Stormont "can't simply
OL,16,Fbe the Sinn Fein mantra: 'Blame it on
OL,17,Fthe Brits".
OL,19,F"We deserve better, we deserve mature
OL,20,Fand sustainable solutions, we deserve
OL,21,Fpolitics which works," he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@IO]wD@XOUxD@NrryD@JO]{D@AOU}D@
OL,26,AVO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
