OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783964952
OL,3,COrange Order urges 'PM in waiting'
OL,4,CBurnham to address 'challenges to the
OL,5,CUnion'
OL,7,F"Will Andy Burnham listen? We don't
OL,8,Fknow ` but Manchester is closer to
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland than Downing Street
OL,10,Fand his attitude could not be any
OL,11,Fworse than the current Secretary of
OL,12,FState.
OL,14,F"Hilary Benn has been a huge
OL,15,Fdisappointment and our initial hopes
OL,16,Ffor a fair hearing, and at least some
OL,17,Faction, were soon dashed.
OL,19,F"He has been so inactive and aloof, he
OL,20,Fhas almost been invisible."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU|D@[O]
